description: Contains intents that manage root stuff of Project Alice

intents.name: UserRandomAnswer
intents.description: The user answer with something random

intents.name: SwitchLanguage
utterances: i want to speak {japanese:=>ToLang} with you

intents.name: StopListening
intents.description: The user asks Alice to not react anymore for a given time
utterances: let us in peace {for an hour:=>Duration}
can you let us in peace {for 30 minutes:=>Duration}

slots.name: Duration
slots.description: How long to ignore the requests

intents.name: AddComponent
intents.description: The user asks to add a new device for Alice to manage
utterances: add a new {tasmota:=>Hardware} {switch:=>EspType} in the {living room:=>Room}
add a {tasmota:=>Hardware} of type {switch:=>EspType} in the {kitchen:=>Room}
i would like to add a {tasmota:=>Hardware} in the {bathroom:=>Room}
can you add a {switch:=>EspType} {tasmota:=>Hardware} in the {bedroom:=>Room}
could you add a new {alice:=>Hardware} device
can you add an {esp:=>Hardware} device please
be ready for a new {esp:=>Hardware} device
can you please add a {switch:=>EspType} based on {esp:=>Hardware}
add a new {esp:=>Hardware} device of type {pir:=>EspType}
i want to register a new {satellite:=>Hardware}
adding a new component to your system
listen for new device connection please
can your add a new device please
i wish to add a new device please
i'm adding a new {satellite:=>Hardware} to your array
let's add a device to your network
i want to add a device to your network

slots.name: Room
slots.description: The room to add the device to

intents.name: DoAliceUpdate
utterances: can you do an {OS:=>WhatToUpdate} update please

intents.name: AnswerEspType
intents.description: The user answers the type of ESP device he wants to add

intents.name: AnswerHardwareType
intents.description: The user answers the hardware type to add

intents.name: AnswerRoom
intents.description: User answers with a room name

intents.name: AnswerWakewordCutting
intents.description: User tells Alice to trim the wakeword a bit more or less

intents.name: CallWakeword
intents.description: User speaks the Hey Alice wakeword

intents.name: AddNewUser
utterances: can you add a new user please
i need to add a new {admin:=>UserAccessLevel}
could you add a new user to your database
here's someone new I'd like you to know
i have someone for you to add as a new user

intents.name: AnswerAccessLevel
intents.description: User answers with an access level
